"{\"uid\": \"cityam.com-sodexo-live-royal-ascot-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Featured Submit a story Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Featured Submit\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 15}, {\"ngram\": \"a story\", \"from\": 16, \"to\": 23}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 29, \"to\": 31}, {\"ngram\": \"your story\", \"from\": 32, \"to\": 42}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured Submit a story Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Featured Submit\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 62}, {\"ngram\": \"a story\", \"from\": 63, \"to\": 70}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 76, \"to\": 78}, {\"ngram\": \"your story\", \"from\": 79, \"to\": 89}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured Submit a story Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Featured Submit\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 109}, {\"ngram\": \"a story\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 117}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 125}, {\"ngram\": \"your story\", \"from\": 126, \"to\": 136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By:Bethany Wales From theParis Olympicsand the Rugby World Cup to Royal Ascot, Sodexo Live has become the invisible force keeping plates loaded and champagne glasses topped up at Europe's biggest events.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 208, \"end\": 219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ascot_Racecourse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0929193064732435e-39, \"text\": \"Royal Ascot\", \"types\": [\"Q1777138\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ascot_Racecourse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ascot_Racecourse\"}, {\"begin\": 221, \"end\": 227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bethany Wales\", \"from\": 144, \"to\": 157}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympicsand\", \"from\": 163, \"to\": 183}, {\"ngram\": \"the Rugby World Cup\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 203}, {\"ngram\": \"the invisible force\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 262}, {\"ngram\": \"plates\", \"from\": 271, \"to\": 277}, {\"ngram\": \"champagne glasses\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 306}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe's biggest events\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2023 the Paris-headquarteredcatering giant's events division, Sodexo Live, served more than 11m guests in the UK alone, employing around 1,700 people across the country to keep its operations running.\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 412, \"end\": 418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}, {\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.961897908133319, \"rank\": 0.039611367843202384, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris-headquarteredcatering giant's events division\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 410}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 11m guests\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 452}, {\"ngram\": \"around 1,700 people\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 518}, {\"ngram\": \"its operations\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And despite a tough couple of years that saw the Covid-19 pandemic wipe out live events, Sodexo's London-headquartered UK arm has rebounded in spectacular fashion, reporting record turnover of \\u00a31.4bn in the year ending August 31, 2023, up from \\u00a31.2bn in the same period of 2019, according to itsmost recently-filed accounts.\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 641, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}, {\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.961897908133319, \"rank\": 0.039611367843202384, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tough couple\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 587}, {\"ngram\": \"the Covid-19\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"live events\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"spectacular fashion\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 714}, {\"ngram\": \"record turnover\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 763}, {\"ngram\": \"the same period\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"itsmost recently-filed accounts\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 875}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This increase in sales has delivered a much-needed boost to the company's recovering bottom line, with its pre-tax profit reaching \\u00a351m in its latest financial year, inching closer to the \\u00a382m it hit in the 12 months ending August 31, 2019.\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 1118, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This increase\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"sales\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 900}, {\"ngram\": \"a much-needed boost\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"the company's recovering bottom line\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"its pre-tax profit\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00a351m\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"its latest financial year\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"the 12 months\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But according to Claire Morris, Sodexo Live's UK CEO, returning to its pre-pandemic profit levels is just the starting point for the company's ambitious growth plans.\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1144, \"end\": 1150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"score\": 0.9999995022896075, \"rank\": 4.976997863873674e-07, \"text\": \"Morris\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\"}, {\"begin\": 1152, \"end\": 1158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}, {\"begin\": 1166, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.961897908133319, \"rank\": 0.039611367843202384, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its pre-pandemic profit levels\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1217}, {\"ngram\": \"just the starting point\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"the company's ambitious growth plans\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay ahead with our three daily briefings delivering all the key market moves, top business and political stories, and incisive analysis straight to your inbox.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our three daily briefings\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"all the key market moves\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"top business\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1379}, {\"ngram\": \"political stories\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"incisive analysis\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1424}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Growth is absolutely a top priority for us and it's going to happen in two ways\\\", she said.\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Growth\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1457}, {\"ngram\": \"a top priority\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1486}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"two ways\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Firstly we are out there to win new clients which is about showing them our proven track record of delivering what we say we will.\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new clients\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"our proven track record\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Secondly, we are going to focus on enhancing our services for existing clients.\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our services\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1735}, {\"ngram\": \"existing clients\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, if we are already providing retail services, we can expand our offerings to include hospitality, and vice versa.\\\"\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"retail services\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1814}, {\"ngram\": \"our offerings\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1843}, {\"ngram\": \"hospitality\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This strategy was demonstrated recently when Sodexo Live's long-time client,Hampden Park stadium in Glasgow, asked the firm to take over the running of its non-match day events in addition to the retail and hospitality it provides during games.\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1931, \"end\": 1937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}, {\"begin\": 1986, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9999999995220605, \"rank\": 4.676371195453658e-10, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This strategy\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1899}, {\"ngram\": \"Hampden Park stadium\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1982}, {\"ngram\": \"the firm\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2009}, {\"ngram\": \"the running\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"its non-match day events\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2074}, {\"ngram\": \"the retail\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2088}, {\"ngram\": \"hospitality\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Morris said: \\\"Our work at Hampden Park is a great example of how we can work with clients to identify their pain points and say OK, here's a different way we can help you reach your goals.\\\"\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2132, \"end\": 2138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"score\": 0.9999995022896075, \"rank\": 4.976997863873674e-07, \"text\": \"Morris\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our work\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"Hampden Park\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"a great example\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"clients\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"their pain points\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2251}, {\"ngram\": \"OK\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2262}, {\"ngram\": \"a different way\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2286}, {\"ngram\": \"your goals\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With such a broad range of clients looking for everything from fast food to Michelin star dining, Morris said the key to Sodexo Live's success has been its ability to shape shift.\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2399, \"end\": 2412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michelin star\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\"}, {\"begin\": 2421, \"end\": 2427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"score\": 0.9999995022896075, \"rank\": 4.976997863873674e-07, \"text\": \"Morris\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\"}, {\"begin\": 2444, \"end\": 2450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a broad range\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"clients\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2357}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2380}, {\"ngram\": \"fast food\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2395}, {\"ngram\": \"the key\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2440}, {\"ngram\": \"its ability\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2486}, {\"ngram\": \"shift\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The company'sRoyal Ascotoffering is the perfect example of this superpower.\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The company'sRoyal\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2522}, {\"ngram\": \"Ascotoffering\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2536}, {\"ngram\": \"the perfect example\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2559}, {\"ngram\": \"this superpower\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the most recent five day meeting Sodexo Live provided catering for more than 250,000 people across 20 restaurants, made possible by at least 3,500 members of staff per day.\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most recent five day meeting\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2620}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 250,000 people\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2679}, {\"ngram\": \"20 restaurants\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2701}, {\"ngram\": \"at least 3,500 members\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2742}, {\"ngram\": \"staff\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2751}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Morris said: \\\"Those five days are the pinnacle of the British summer event's calendar and we have to make sure there is something for everyone.\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2762, \"end\": 2768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"score\": 0.9999995022896075, \"rank\": 4.976997863873674e-07, \"text\": \"Morris\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\"}, {\"begin\": 2816, \"end\": 2823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999840079, \"rank\": 1.5787416398787315e-08, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those five days\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2791}, {\"ngram\": \"the pinnacle\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2808}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2891}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We operate four different enclosures, with the Royal enclosure at the premium end.\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 2990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2955, \"end\": 2970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fasil_Ghebbi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Royal enclosure\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fasil_Ghebbi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fasil_Ghebbi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four different enclosures\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 2944}, {\"ngram\": \"the premium end\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 2989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's where you are seeing guests in their top hats and tails who are paying for hospitality.\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 3085, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"guests\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"their top hats\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3043}, {\"ngram\": \"tails\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3053}, {\"ngram\": \"hospitality\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Within that they have a choice of restaurants run by chefs like Simon Rogan, who has three Michelin stars, and of course our long-standing partner Raymond Blanc.\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3179, \"end\": 3187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"score\": 0.999613755119758, \"rank\": 0.0003863941227750781, \"text\": \"Michelin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\"}, {\"begin\": 3235, \"end\": 3248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Blanc\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Raymond Blanc\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Blanc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Blanc\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a choice\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3118}, {\"ngram\": \"restaurants\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3133}, {\"ngram\": \"chefs\", \"from\": 3141, \"to\": 3146}, {\"ngram\": \"Simon Rogan\", \"from\": 3152, \"to\": 3163}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Guests can also opt for a high-end retail option which is going to include things like steak sandwiches or a luxury afternoon tea so it's still in keeping with the environment.\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3428, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Guests\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3258}, {\"ngram\": \"a high-end retail option\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3300}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3327, \"to\": 3333}, {\"ngram\": \"steak sandwiches\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3355}, {\"ngram\": \"a luxury afternoon tea\", \"from\": 3359, \"to\": 3381}, {\"ngram\": \"the environment\", \"from\": 3412, \"to\": 3427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then in the Queen Anne enclosure you are going to see mainly retail offerings but guests also have the option to buy a hospitality experience with Lisa Goodwin Allen, who also has a Michelin star.\", \"from\": 3430, \"to\": 3627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3578, \"end\": 3582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9999997987593108, \"rank\": 2.0124066365915079e-07, \"text\": \"Lisa\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Simpson\"}, {\"begin\": 3591, \"end\": 3596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\", \"score\": 0.9999999998403837, \"rank\": 1.5711622628589128e-10, \"text\": \"Allen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\"}, {\"begin\": 3613, \"end\": 3626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michelin star\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Queen Anne enclosure\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3463}, {\"ngram\": \"mainly retail offerings\", \"from\": 3485, \"to\": 3508}, {\"ngram\": \"guests\", \"from\": 3513, \"to\": 3519}, {\"ngram\": \"the option\", \"from\": 3530, \"to\": 3540}, {\"ngram\": \"a hospitality experience\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People looking for something more low-key are also going to find what they are looking for across our retail kiosks, whether that's a cup of coffee or a flute of champagne.\\\"\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3636}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3658}, {\"ngram\": \"our retail kiosks\", \"from\": 3728, \"to\": 3745}, {\"ngram\": \"a cup\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3767}, {\"ngram\": \"coffee\", \"from\": 3771, \"to\": 3777}, {\"ngram\": \"a flute\", \"from\": 3781, \"to\": 3788}, {\"ngram\": \"champagne\", \"from\": 3792, \"to\": 3801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Sodexo Live, evolving in line with changing consumer expectations has been key to its longevity.\", \"from\": 3805, \"to\": 3905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3809, \"end\": 3815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"line\", \"from\": 3834, \"to\": 3838}, {\"ngram\": \"changing consumer expectations\", \"from\": 3844, \"to\": 3874}, {\"ngram\": \"its longevity\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 3904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Morris said that as people's budgets have become tighter due to the rising cost of living, the threshold for what counts as good value for money has also been raised.\", \"from\": 3907, \"to\": 4073, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3907, \"end\": 3913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"score\": 0.9999995022896075, \"rank\": 4.976997863873674e-07, \"text\": \"Morris\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people's budgets\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 3943}, {\"ngram\": \"the rising cost\", \"from\": 3971, \"to\": 3986}, {\"ngram\": \"living\", \"from\": 3990, \"to\": 3996}, {\"ngram\": \"the threshold\", \"from\": 3998, \"to\": 4011}, {\"ngram\": \"good value\", \"from\": 4031, \"to\": 4041}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 4046, \"to\": 4051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"People do not want to wait in queues and they definitely do not want to miss whatever event they are attending because they are stuck in line for their drinks.\\\"\", \"from\": 4075, \"to\": 4246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 4086, \"to\": 4092}, {\"ngram\": \"queues\", \"from\": 4116, \"to\": 4122}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever event\", \"from\": 4163, \"to\": 4177}, {\"ngram\": \"line\", \"from\": 4223, \"to\": 4227}, {\"ngram\": \"their drinks\", \"from\": 4232, \"to\": 4244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To help its staff keep up, Sodexo Live has invested heavily in technology over the past few years, including at Brighton & Hove Albion Football Club, where the company operates food and beverage kiosks.\", \"from\": 4248, \"to\": 4450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4275, \"end\": 4281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229